468
00:32:36,232 --> 00:32:38,211
Return it to me when your financial situation improves.

469
00:32:40,380 --> 00:32:41,368
But...

470
00:32:41,906 --> 00:32:47,410
I know you don’t like me very much.

471
00:32:49,045 --> 00:32:54,312
But please know that I never wanted to replace your mother.

472
00:32:56,165 --> 00:32:56,967
Take it.

473
00:32:58,085 --> 00:32:58,680
Come on.

474
00:33:00,265 --> 00:33:00,905
Keep it.

475
00:33:01,367 --> 00:33:02,502
Don’t lose it.

476
00:33:02,872 --> 00:33:03,407
I won’t.

477
00:33:05,712 --> 00:33:06,413
Aunt Nipa,

478
