496
00:34:50,484 --> 00:34:52,362
Yes. You were amazing.

497
00:34:53,896 --> 00:34:56,480
How about…

498
00:34:58,080 --> 00:34:59,979
you come here and play Water Boxing with me every year.

499
00:35:00,982 --> 00:35:06,245
I’ll let you beat me every time.

500
00:35:09,194 --> 00:35:11,115
